URL: 
BugReports: 
Description: Provides tools to download public health datasets from the DATASUS FTP server (ftp.datasus.gov.br), with functions to preprocess, filter, and select variables from the data. The package supports handling large datasets, exporting processed data to DBC or RData formats, and generating log files with detailed records of data extraction and processing steps, supporting reproducible data workflows.
